<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[70323]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA[Oskar Hansen's work comes to Macba]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[Macba is holding a retrospective on this Polish architect and his Open Form theory.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>An exhibition dedicated to the work of the Polish architect Oskar Hansen (1922-2005) focuses on the development of his theory of Open Form.</p>
<p>Hansen created and developed a revolutionary educational system of great potential to develop the creative and rational faculties of individuals and groups. It is considered, within his system, that every individual action must be aimed at enabling responses and involvement from others or the group.</p>
